     HOME AUTOMATION SYSTEM
This project is to build a home automation with alexa,node red,and raspberry pi.

STEPS:
1.get your raspberry pi up and running
2.update your system and install node-red if not already on pi
3.sign up @ node-red alexa home skill bridge
4.login and creat your devices
5.to launch node-red,open terminal and type in this command 'node-red-start'
copy the ip address from the terminal with the given port number
6.clone this repo and inport it into the node-red
NOTE:before you do,change the username from the file
7.in the node-red,configure the home assistant node with your credentials
8.download alexa app on your phone and configure it
9.link the the node-red to your alexa
voala!!!! enjoy
